---
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---
<section class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800" id="contact">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-20">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <div class="mb-6 max-w-3xl text-center sm:text-center md:mx-auto md:mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 font-bold tracking-tight text-primary text-3xl sm:text-5xl">
          Servicio Técnico de Electrodomésticos en Tenerife Sur
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          Reparación de electrodomésticos a domicilio en toda la isla. 
          Servicio técnico oficial multimarca en San Isidro y zona sur de Tenerife.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-stretch justify-center">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="h-full pr-6">
          <p class="mt-3 mb-12 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Puedes encontrarnos a través de los siguientes medios:
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <li class="flex">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded bg-blue-900 text-gray-50">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6">
                  <path d="M9 11a3 3 0 1 0 6 0a3 3 0 0 0 -6 0"></path>
                  <path d="M17.657 16.657l-4.243 4.243a2 2 0 0 1 -2.827 0l-4.244 -4.243a8 8 0 1 1 11.314 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-primary">Nuestra Dirección</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">C. la Vera, 10, Local 1 Bajo</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">38611 San Isidro, Santa Cruz de Tenerife</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded bg-blue-900 text-gray-50">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6">
                  <path d="M5 4h4l2 5l-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5l1.5 -2.5l5 2v4a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2a16 16 0 0 1 -15 -15a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-primary">Teléfono</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                  <a href="tel:+34603403094" class="text-current">603 40 30 94</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded bg-blue-900 text-gray-50">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6">
                  <path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 0 0 -18 0"></path>
                  <path d="M12 7v5l3 3"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-primary">Horario</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">Lunes - Domingo</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">9:00 - 17:00</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card h-fit max-w-6xl p-5 md:p-12" id="form">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">¿Necesitas un presupuesto?</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Envíanos un mensaje o llámanos directamente. Te atenderemos lo antes posible.
          </p>
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1480.065759071561!2d-16.563350191974155!3d28.079152960505645!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xc6a9f8485f185c3%3A0x490be0bd58e17f6f!2sReparaci%C3%B3n%20y%20recuperaci%C3%B3n%20de%20electrodom%C3%A9sticos%20Tenerife.%20S.S.TORRES!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1731856460699!5m2!1ses!2ses" 
            width="100%" 
            height="450" 
            style="border:0;" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
